        <name>tasker-modal-prompt-UIPages.css</name>
        <style>/* Use this CSS to style Tasker modal prompt UI Pages. &#13;
The UI Page will need this Name added to the jelly to create a &lt;link&gt; tag.&#13;
UI Pages using this CSS are:&#13;
    delete_task_prompt&#13;
    reopen_task_prompt&#13;
&#13;
*** NOW UI Pages use Heisenberg style sheet which may differ slightly from Bootstrap's style&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
2.7.0 | 2021-08-29 | mmcc | STRY0107404 - Draft Scheduled Tasks – UI – Delete Modal &#13;
Put into a style sheet&#13;
2.7.0 | 2021-09-03 | mmcc | DFCT0010476 - "Acknowledgement Prompt" does not have an "Acknowledge" button so users cannot use Tasker&#13;
  Dropped class modal-footer; Added class .dtech-modal-widget-body&#13;
  Change class dtech-modal-footer to dtech-modal-widget-footer and updated to have padding-top to reduce white space and position since body sets it as well&#13;
2.7.0 | 2021-09-14 | mmcc | STRY0099532 - DIA- 'Mass Reopen' Task Tree Modal (MVP)&#13;
  Renamed to be more generic&#13;
  Added vertical align for the radio button label&#13;
  Changed $tasker-delete-prompt-perm-delete to use $tasker-modal-prompt-standard-text-color&#13;
  Changed CSS Selector .dtech-perm-delete to use .dtech-standard-text-color&#13;
2.7.0 | 2021-09-22 | mmcc | STRY0108861 - DIA- Cancel from Top Task Notification &#13;
  Added CSS Selector asterisk&#13;
  Added disabled for submit and primary button (Reopen)&#13;
  Added disabled for submit and danger button (Cancel)&#13;
&#13;
*/&#13;
&#13;
#submit.btn-primary[disabled] {&#13;
    color: #ffffff;&#13;
    background-color: #1f8476;&#13;
    border-color: #10463f;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
#submit.btn-danger[disabled] {&#13;
    color: #ffffff;&#13;
    background-color: #c83c36;&#13;
    border-color: #a0302b;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
.asterisk::before {&#13;
   color: red;&#13;
   content: "*";&#13;
   position: absolute;&#13;
   margin-left: -1%;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
label.dtech-radio-inline {&#13;
  margin-bottom: 0;&#13;
  margin-top: 5px;&#13;
  vertical-align: middle;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
.dtech-box {&#13;
  display: flex;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
/* Must be a descendant of the class dtech-box */&#13;
.dtech-box .dtech-push-right {&#13;
  margin-left: auto!important;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
/* this was a copy of Bootstrap's modal-body */&#13;
.dtech-modal-widget-body {&#13;
  padding: 15px;&#13;
  position: relative;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
/* this was a copy of Bootstrap's modal-footer */&#13;
.dtech-modal-widget-footer {&#13;
  /* padding 15 to padding top 15 */&#13;
  padding-top: 15px;&#13;
  text-align: right;&#13;
  border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;&#13;
  /* added position */&#13;
  position: relative;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
.dtech-text-center {&#13;
  text-align: center;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
h1 {&#13;
  color: #ff9800;  /* $tasker-color-brown-red */&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
/* Future use, when/if SVG's have internal CSS variable for color&#13;
.dtech-warning64 {&#13;
/*  color: $tasker-color-brown-red; */&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
.dtech-max-width-fit-content {&#13;
  max-width: fit-content;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
.dtech-task-name {&#13;
  color: #35363a; /* $tasker-delete-prompt-task-name */&#13;
  margin-bottom: 25px;&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
.dtech-standard-text-color {&#13;
  color: #35363a; /* $tasker-modal-prompt-standard-text-color */&#13;
}&#13;
&#13;
.dtech-subtasks-also-deleted {&#13;
  color: #0087D2; /* $tasker-delete-prompt-subtasks-also-deleted */&#13;
  margin-left: 5px;&#13;
}&#13;
</style>
